<font face="Verdana" color="#D0B078" size="3"><b>Chat and Log-in server downtime</b></font> 
<br>
<font face="Verdana" size="1" color="#FFFFFF">Posted: Sunday, August 27 by <a href="mailto:vumil@brellserilis.net">Vumil</a> @ 2:50 AM EDT<br>
<font face="Verdana" size="1" color="#FFFFFF">
Add a <a href="http://www.brellserilis.net/news/talkback/967362635,57955,.html">comment</a> on this article [0 Comments]</font><br>

