<br><br><font face="Verdana" size="2"> We're going to be making some changes soon, pretty radical ones, in order to get these boards to the point that they both serve the customer and Verant. I hope it works, but then it may fail, in which case I doubt the boards will be around long. <br><br>We'll certainly give it a shot though. <br><br>-Brad</font><br><br><br>
