<br><br><font face="Verdana" size="2"> <b>Source: Everlore</b><br><br>At 2pm Pacific Time on July the 31st, Maladwen the Rogue will hold the first annual Kithicor Hunt for a werewolf. Contestants must submit 10pp per lvl as a fee, then they are released at 9 at night. As the sun sets, the higher levels are released first, then the lower levels. The first person to despose of one werewolf, shall get the pot. <br><br>If you are killed by anything, you are immediatley disqualified from the tournament. The tournament shall also not begin until the pot is full with at least 90-100pp. The winner of this shall promptly get the entire pot. <br></font><br><br><br>
