<font face="Verdana" color="#D0B078" size="3"><b>Velious Feature List</b></font> 
<br>
<font face="Verdana" size="1" color="#FFFFFF">Posted: Tuesday, July 11 by <a href="mailto:delsonora@brellserilis.net">Delsonora</a> @ 2:32 PM EDT<br>
<font face="Verdana" size="1" color="#FFFFFF">
Add a <a href="http://www.brellserilis.net/news/talkback/963343924,99846,.html">comment</a> on this article [0 Comments]</font><br>

<br><br><font face="Verdana" size="2"> Some tid bits about Velious, the upcoming Everquest expansion, that have been gathered during EG3 in Vegas. Also, first reported on Everlore.<br><br>* One new Continent - Velious which contains 12 new zones. <br>* Brand new character graphics. <br>* Velious will be geared towards levels 35-60 players, although the level limit will stay at 60. <br>* New Starting City for Barbarians. <br>* Velious will focus primarily on new zones, quests, items and more variety in how players appear in-game. <br>* Some of the new creatures include White Dragons, and frost & storm giants although there will be no new player races or classes. <br>* Official Velious site will be up in about a month or so, will include screen shots. <br>* Currently set for a Release Date of December 2000.<br></font><br><br><br>
