<font face="Verdana" color="#D0B078" size="3"><b>VELIOUS ANNOUNCED</b></font> 
<br>
<font face="Verdana" size="1" color="#FFFFFF">Posted: Sunday, July 9 by <a href="mailto:vumil@brellserilis.net">Vumil</a> @ 10:52 PM EDT<br>
<font face="Verdana" size="1" color="#FFFFFF">
Add a <a href="http://www.brellserilis.net/news/talkback/963201179,42259,.html">comment</a> on this article [1 Comments]</font><br>

