<br><br><font face="Verdana" size="2"> Friday, June 16th,  there will be an official GM run tournament in the Lake Rathe arena. The event is called the Test of  Mystics. It is for necromancers, mages, wizards and enchanters of any level. Entrance fees are 10 plat multiplied by your level. Each player will be completely debuffed before the match, but is allowed 3 pre-combat spells. If a pet is summoned it counts as 2 of the 3 spells. <br><br>Sounds like a lot of fun guys. There will be prizes for the winners, but none have been announced. Good luck!<br><br>For more information: <a href="http://everquest.station.sony.com/n_cal_current.html">Official Everquest Events Calendar</a><br><br><br><br><br></font><br><br><br>
