<font face="Verdana" color="#D0B078" size="3"><b>Venril Sathir Wipeout!</b></font> 
<br>
<font face="Verdana" size="1" color="#FFFFFF">Posted: Monday, June 12 by <a href="mailto:jester1176@home.com">Gunganus</a> @ 2:15 PM EDT<br>
<font face="Verdana" size="1" color="#FFFFFF">
Add a <a href="http://www.brellserilis.net/news/talkback/960837316,87025,.html">comment</a> on this article [0 Comments]</font><br>

<br><br><font face="Verdana" size="2"> On Saturday, June 10th, the Legion of Heroes guild attempted a raid of Karnors with a specific target in mind; Venril Sathir. Kassim Silverblade led a group of over 30 friends into his lair. When the group charged his room, they were met by Venril and some healers. The group fought hard, but unfortunately was wiped out. Venril was being healed all the while by clerics through the walls. Although this was a defeat, the Legion of Heroes took it as a learning experience and will try again, I'm sure.<br><br>Picture:<a href="http://www.brellserilis.net/images/kunark/LoHVenril.gif">Venril Sathir</a><br></font><br><br><br>
