<br><br><font face="Verdana" size="2"> When a character reaches his or her 20th season, one of the great points of pride is the selection of a surname. In my opinion, the surname filter is a little TOO picky (rejected almost every surname I have ever chosen including the one i use now, Blackthorne, until a GM could do it manually). Well, this player, frustrated with being told their surname was illegal decided to protest this. It is amazing what the surname rejects and what it accepts, isnt it?<br><br>Image: <a href="http://www.brellserilis.net/images/adanesurname.gif">Tell us how you really feel Adane ;)</a><br></font><br><br><br>
