<br><br><font face="Verdana" size="2"> Just some words about the JBoots quest. I was fortunate enough while hunting with my longtime partner Trompe in SRO to stumble upon the Ancient Cyclops. After killing the beast and obtaining the ring (sorry to the mage who was also searching for the clops!) i set out to finish the rest of the quest for the Journeyman boots. Well, appears Hasten hasn't spawned in like, a week. Brother Z is running around and nowhere to be found is Hasten. After talking with a Guide, they said the problem was being worked on but in true Verant style, No ETA. Hopefully after the server reset tomorrow, Hasten will be back. Several players have devised cute ways to alleviate the boredeom of waiting for this spawn, which i have included a shot of for your enjoyment.<br><br>I have also found a picture of what a complete suit of Flayed Skin armor looks like and made a link. Source was Castersrealm.<br><br>Image: <a href="http://www.brellserilis.net/images/encumbered.gif">One encumbered gnome!</a><br>Image: <a href="http://www.brellserilis.net/images/bored.gif">Bored to Death Waiting on Hasten</a><br>Image: <a href="http://eq.castersrealm.com/images/flayed.jpg">Flayed Skin Armor</a></font><br><br><br>
