<br>
<font face="Verdana" size="1" color="#FFFFFF">Posted: Tuesday, May 23 by <a href="mailto:delsonora@brellserilis.net">Delsonora</a> @ 3:02 PM EDT<br>
<font face="Verdana" size="1" color="#FFFFFF">
Add a <a href="http://www.brellserilis.net/news/talkback/959112159,50890,.html">comment</a> on this article [0 Comments]</font><br>

<br><br><font face="Verdana" size="2"> In the last patch (and also in the zone patch last night for many Kunark zones) there were some changes to various factions and experience tables.<br><br>* Spirocs are now connected to the Aviak faction (killing Spirocs further lowers Aviak faction) which also is connected to the baby Aviaks by the Arena zone in Lake Rathetear. <br><br>* Ogres in Timorous Deep are now connected to Venril Sathir faction<br><br>* Many of the Kunark zones were given enhanced experience. Many are reporting Karnor's for instance yields greater exp than before.<br><br>* Raptors in the Timurous Deep zone now can see invis and will aggro on you.<br><br>* Cannibalize II quest is back in the game<br></font><br><br><br>
