<br><br><font face="Verdana" size="2"> Well a couple of items for today. The first is i am pleased to announce Vumil and Goat are now Administrators (donated by the Avatar of Brell) of the Brell Message Boards. What this means is they will be doing a lot of the day-to-day checking up on the boards, moderating tasks and planning for new forums or removing dead forums as needed. Pretty much what they have done before thrown in with a couple of things I primarily handled in the past. The boards have grown so much in the past year and it wouldn't be possible to have if they weren't lending their assistance, so thanks guys.<br><br>The second thing to report is that there will be some slight changes over the next couple weeks to this site. As anyone who has experience with web site development knows, as your site grows you begin to see areas that need to be improved. I have seen lots of places i can improve the site and taken lots and lots of feedback from everyone (thanks). <br></font><br><br><br>
