<font face="Verdana" color="#D0B078" size="3"><b>Plane of Sky: Isle 4 clearing</b></font> 
<br>
<font face="Verdana" size="1" color="#FFFFFF">Posted: Sunday, May 21 by <a href="mailto:vumil@brellserilis.net">Vumil</a> @ 8:56 AM EDT<br>
<font face="Verdana" size="1" color="#FFFFFF">
Add a <a href="http://www.brellserilis.net/news/talkback/958917390,47972,.html">comment</a> on this article [1 Comments]</font><br>

<br><br><font face="Verdana" size="2"> Island 4 of the Plane of Sky was cleared by Silent Redemption and friends late last night.  Isle 4 consists of 3 Essence Carriors and 3 Essence Harvesters which are all level 52.  Kill one of them and it splits into 2 level 54 offspring, kill one of the level 54 offspring and it spawns 1 level 56 offspring.  They are all quite long fights resulting in a few deaths from each(usually rangers *grin*).  Once 3 of these Essence Carriors or Essence Harvesters are killed the Keeper of Souls spawns(level 60+ boss of the island).  He DT's(death touches) and hits for around 360.  <br><br><b>Loot obtained:</b><br>3 SK belt's - 8ac 5str 5MR .1wt Effect: Haste<br>2 Ranger Belt's - 6ac 5wis 5str 5sv vs dis .1wt Effect: Haste<br>Monk Belt - 4ac 5str 5dex 5sv vs cold .1wt Effect: Haste<br>Bracelet of Quiescence - 7cha 7int 20mana, Enchanter only<br><br><a href="http://www.brellserilis.net/images/sky/pos1.gif">Keeper of Souls</a><br><a href="http://www.brellserilis.net/images/sky/pos2.gif">Keeper of Souls Corpse</a><br><a href="http://www.brellserilis.net/images/sky/isle5.gif">Isle 5 Spirocs</a><br><a href="http://www.brellserilis.net/images/sky/isle5.2.gif">Isle 5 Guardian</a></font><br><br><br>
