<font face="Verdana" color="#D0B078" size="3"><b>Brell Guild Merry Band on  EQLizer</b></font> 
<br>
<font face="Verdana" size="1" color="#FFFFFF">Posted: Thursday, May 18 by <a href="mailto:delsonora@brellserilis.net">Delsonora</a> @ 12:06 PM EDT<br>
<font face="Verdana" size="1" color="#FFFFFF">
