<a name="newsitem958668563,56336,"></a>
<font face="Verdana" color="#D0B078" size="3"><b>From the horses mouth (couple news items)</b></font> 
<br>
<font face="Verdana" size="1" color="#FFFFFF">Posted: Thursday, May 18 by <a href="mailto:delsonora@brellserilis.net">Delsonora</a> @ 11:49 AM EDT<br>
<font face="Verdana" size="1" color="#FFFFFF">
Add a <a href="http://www.brellserilis.net/news/talkback/958668563,56336,.html">comment</a> on this article [0 Comments]</font><br>

<br><br><font face="Verdana" size="2"> Couple news items from Abashi that were posted on the Everquest board, i have cut and snipped them here for convenience.<br><br>Enchanter Illusions<br>-------------------<br>No new illusions are planned for enchanters at this time.<br><br>-Gordon<br><br>Ranger Balance Issues (no defense upgrades past 50)<br>---------------------------------------------------<br>The whole ranger-defense thing is coming from the logic that: At 50 they are balanced. At 60 everyone else gets bonuses to defense, and rangers don't, therefore they aren't balanced.<br><br>The problem with this logic is that we don't balance classes on a skill-by-skill basis. We balance them as a complete offering. Everything that a class has is part of the equation. The fact that skill-point allocations, ratios, and percentage change as you go level to level is not in and of itself indicative of an imbalance. <br><br>-Gordon<br><br>Item weight for monks and SK<br>----------------------------<br>I'm having some of the weights on Monk stuff looked at today. In other news, Darkforge armor (SK) is having its weight lowered, and should go live the next time we patch items.<br><br>-Gordon<br><br>Spawn times (specifically Treant Fists quest)<br>----------------------------------------------<br>A 72 minute spawn seems ok. Quests for items aren't supposed to give instant gratification. I think that one of the problems we are running into is that when people want an item, they want the item NOW, and any time that it takes to get the item is considered a camp. <br><br>Things need to take time, or the prestige that comes with having is gone.<br><br>-Gordon<br><br></font><br><br><br>
<a name="newsitem958667978,15521,"></a>
<font face="Verdana" color="#D0B078" size="3"><b>Patch Day</b></font> 
<br>
<font face="Verdana" size="1" color="#FFFFFF">Posted: Thursday, May 18 by <a href="mailto:delsonora@brellserilis.net">Delsonora</a> @ 11:39 AM EDT<br>
