<font face="Verdana" color="#D0B078" size="3"><b>Level 51+ Spells not dropping</b></font> 
<br>
<font face="Verdana" size="1" color="#FFFFFF">Posted: Monday, May 15 by <a href="mailto:Taeolin@brellserilis.net">Taeolin</a> @ 1:10 PM EDT<br>
<font face="Verdana" size="1" color="#FFFFFF">
Add a <a href="http://www.brellserilis.net/news/talkback/958414240,3309,.html">comment</a> on this article [0 Comments]</font><br>

<br><br><font face="Verdana" size="2"> The level 50+ spells so many casters are trying to get their hands on are not dropping as planned. Gordon confirmed the bug officially on the Gameplay board:<br><br>          Well I got some time late Wednesday and went into an area that is supposed to be pretty-well saturated with the new  spells, whacked about 250 critters, and didn't find any spells. So I'm not completely convinced that they are dropping correctly any longer. I'll get back with you.<br><br>                     -Gordon<br><br>As for an ETA on the fix, Gordon had the following to say:<br><br>          Monday is probably the soonest we'll see some action on this. Everyone who can fix it is up at E3 looking after our booth. I'm trying to find out now if the correct data is on the servers but just not activated. If that's the case, we could probably fix it before then. <br><br>                     -Gordon</font><br><br><br>
