<font face="Verdana" color="#D0B078" size="3"><b>Aradune on Level 51+ Spells</b></font> 
<br>
<font face="Verdana" size="1" color="#FFFFFF">Posted: Monday, May 8 by <a href="mailto:delsonora@brellserilis.net">Delsonora</a> @ 4:09 PM EDT<br>
<font face="Verdana" size="1" color="#FFFFFF">
Add a <a href="http://www.brellserilis.net/news/talkback/957820176,50489,.html">comment</a> on this article [0 Comments]</font><br>

<br><br><font face="Verdana" size="2"> This has been answered, but I'll answer again.<br><br>Scrolls are dropping.<br><br>Many dungeons have not been explored and/or are barely touched.<br><br>People tend to move together and to focus on certain areas, especially when areas are new. Currently, most players are in a minority of the mid and high level dungeons in Kunark.<br><br>We did NOT make each dungeon in Kunark 'one stop shopping'. Some are better for casters, some better for melee, some mixed.<br><br>Also, high level spells drop on high level NPCs. Players ARE finding spells, but they are hard to get, and in dungeons. <br><br>-Brad<br><br></font><br><br><br>
