<br><br><font face="Verdana" size="2"> Well, finally a new caster only robe was found on Kunark. As posted on Casters Realm, the robe is called the Froglock Bone Casters robe. It looks like a SMR (Shiny Metallic Robe) except black and dark green. The stats are pretty nice, +8 str, +8 int, +40mana +10 sv fire +10 sv magic and AC 10.<br><br>Image: <a href="http://eq.castersrealm.com/images/frogrobe.jpg">Froglock Bonecaster's Robe</a><br>Image: <a href="http://eq.castersrealm.com/images/frogrobeworn.jpg">Dark Elf wearing robe</a><br></font><br><br><br>
