<br><br><font face="Verdana" size="2"> Tassadar Presents: the Harpers Comedy Festival<br>       <br>Friday, May 26, at 9PM EST at Lake Rathetear Arena.<br><br>The Festivities are expected to last about three hours.<br>There will be a raffle for the spectators to participate in at 5pp per ticket. <br><br>All the performers who register ahead will be automaically entered into a random drawing for an EB Mace 8/28 1HB.<br>The following prizes will be awarded on merit by our panel of judges; First prize 1000pp, Second prize 500pp, Third prize 250pp, and five Honorable mentions of 50pp.<br><br>Performers are asked to limit their routines to a maximum of 15 minutes, and that the content be Everquest related. <br><br>Automatic Disqualifaction will occur for Graphic Sexual Content, Heavy Profanity, and Disrupting Another Contestant's Performance.<br>There will be an 'open mike' after all registered performers have finished for those who wish to try their hand.<br><br>Those who participate in the 'open mike' time will not be elegible for the drawing, but will be elegible for judged prizes.<br><br>**Those interested in competing should register ahead of time by emailing a registration letter that includes character name and estimated performance length to us at <br><br>> harpers_event@bigfoot.com <**<br><br>A confirmation letter will be sent when your registration is received. <br><br>Thank you,<br>Iecestorm Wendigo <br>Emissary of the Harpers<br></font><br><br><br>
