<br><br><font face="Verdana" size="2"> *Patch Today*<br><br>Today's patch (eqmain.dll) was to correct some Kunark registration problems for overseas customers using the new retail box. In addition, text was updated on the "Kunark Registration" page for those who upgrade using an account key from the retail box. <br><br><br>*Iksar Factions Changing Tomorrow*<br><br>The faction information on the live servers in reference to Iksar and how they interact with other factions outside Kunark is incorrect. Corrections will be going in tomorrow, making the Iksar KOS (Kill on Sight) to pretty much everything on the other continents. We normally wouldn't announce something like this, however we want to give Iksar who may have bound next to or near something that is liable to become KOS to them tomorrow a chance to get away. <br><br>This announcement is not meant to be a free license to go exploring the mainland with your Iksar tonight, and our plans to pre-announce issues such as this in the future hinge on players not taking advantage of the information. We appreciate everyone's cooperation.<br><br></font><br><br><br>
