<br><br><font face="Verdana" size="2"> Just a few noteworthy changes to the board today. Many of you have brought up the point that certain camps dont need to be reserved, due to the fact they can be accomplished impromptu with very few people. Some of these include Mistmoore, Efreeti, Guk etc. Also, not everyone on the server checks the boards or knows about them.<br><br>So, in response to your concerns, i have removed Raids Schedule: all others, from the message board. I would also like to announce the addition of a new discussion board, Kunark Discussion. Its purpose is pretty obvious, to talk about the new expansion pack, expansion zones, etc. I am sure as Kunark is explored, the need for new forums will become relevant. Until then, post Kunark related topics here.<br><br>Thanks!<br></font><br><br><br>
