<br><br><font face="Verdana" size="2"> Okay guys. Several guilds have contacted me asking if they could have a MyGuild.BrellSerilis.net domain name. The answer is yes, the ISP i use does support this, however there is a 1 time fee associated with it. Now, the fee isnt a huge deal -- but i definetly do not want to be paying out of pocket for a domain name alias for every guild who wants one. Which is why I have decided to do the following.<br><br>Whereas originally i was planning on accepting guilds sending in a payment (one-time) for having the alias established, i have decided to issue them as rewards for outstanding guild/server spirit. Helping to publicize the server, this site, the message boards are all examples of things i will consider when giving these aliases away. Taking the time to be a featured guild, and answering some question is another.<br><br>If having a cool website url isnt enough (no need to publicize geocities when you can publicize brellserilis!) this will guarantee your guild a link from the top level page of BrellSerilis.net (this page) and a spot as part of the BrellSerilis.net network! <br><br>If your interested in either of these things then get in contact with me.<br></font><br><br><br>
