<font face="Verdana" color="#D0B078" size="3"><b>Gordon on Inte's Sword of Death</b></font> 
<br>
<font face="Verdana" size="1" color="#FFFFFF">Posted: Thursday, April 13 by <a href="mailto:delsonora@brellserilis.net">Delsonora</a> @ 4:15 PM EDT<br>
<font face="Verdana" size="1" color="#FFFFFF">
Add a <a href="http://www.brellserilis.net/news/talkback/955660558,94570,.html">comment</a> on this article [0 Comments]</font><br>

<br><br><font face="Verdana" size="2"> Inte's Super Duper Sword of Death<br><br>Yeah that 150dmg 15 delay sword was our fault. We wanted Inte to be carrying a flaming sword, and one of the game designers figured that no one would ever be able to kill him and made the sword a little unruly. We did have the forethought to make it NORENT though, and changed the stats in the item database to something a little less nasty, but we went so long without patching items that someone actually managed to kill Inte two days before the patch. <br>That'll teach us to go around calling NPCs unkillable :)<br><br>-Gordon<br></font><br><br><br>
