<font face="Verdana" color="#D0B078" size="3"><b>Paw of Opolla (nixed?)</b></font> 
<br>
<font face="Verdana" size="1" color="#FFFFFF">Posted: Tuesday, April 11 by <a href="mailto:delsonora@brellserilis.net">Delsonora</a> @ 12:14 PM EDT<br>
